{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/creative/checked-shift/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"c3357515-171a-583d-868e-23ae38ce5f8a","excerpt":"首先，大家不要看到我说格子衬衣就觉得我要黑程序员，要知道，我曾经也是程序员。 我产生这个想法的原因，是因为一个叫做 Github 的东西。非程序员可能不太了解 Github…","html":"<p>首先，大家不要看到我说格子衬衣就觉得我要黑程序员，要知道，我曾经也是程序员。</p>\n<p>我产生这个想法的原因，是因为一个叫做 Github 的东西。非程序员可能不太了解 Github，我先简单介绍一下。比如说设计师会有一个网站可以发自己的作品互相交流，那么程序员也会去一个地方发自己的代码互相交流，也就是以码会友，这个地方就是 Github。</p>\n<p>大家可以看一下我的 Github 主页，我把上次帮阿北写的婚礼邀请函代码也放上去了。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/5719827f4fec2821f468900803ed7af0/8ec0a/github.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"github\"\n        title=\"github\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/5719827f4fec2821f468900803ed7af0/c08c5/github.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/5719827f4fec2821f468900803ed7af0/0913d/github.jpg 160w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/5719827f4fec2821f468900803ed7af0/cb69c/github.jpg 320w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/5719827f4fec2821f468900803ed7af0/c08c5/github.jpg 640w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/5719827f4fec2821f468900803ed7af0/6a068/github.jpg 960w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/5719827f4fec2821f468900803ed7af0/eea4a/github.jpg 1280w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/5719827f4fec2821f468900803ed7af0/8ec0a/github.jpg 2560w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>不像设计师把某一个作品放到网上就很少更新了，程序员的项目代码一般是不断更新的，每隔一段时间就会提交一次。比如说我上次给阿北做的邀请函，做了第一版之后阿北又让我改了好几次，所以我是边修改边上传的。那么，程序员就会有提交代码的记录。Github 很贴心，为了让程序员有成就感，会在程序员的主页显示一个提交记录组成的表格，也就是活跃度图表。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/420e863e3b90e45df6936700fb0ac58e/356e8/contributions.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 28.125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"contributions\"\n        title=\"contributions\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/420e863e3b90e45df6936700fb0ac58e/c08c5/contributions.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/420e863e3b90e45df6936700fb0ac58e/0913d/contributions.jpg 160w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/420e863e3b90e45df6936700fb0ac58e/cb69c/contributions.jpg 320w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/420e863e3b90e45df6936700fb0ac58e/c08c5/contributions.jpg 640w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/420e863e3b90e45df6936700fb0ac58e/6a068/contributions.jpg 960w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/420e863e3b90e45df6936700fb0ac58e/eea4a/contributions.jpg 1280w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/420e863e3b90e45df6936700fb0ac58e/356e8/contributions.jpg 1512w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>这是我的活跃度图表，每个格子代表一天，灰色格子表示这一天没有上传代码，绿色表示上传了，而且越绿代表上传的代码次数越多。你从我这个活跃度可以看出，我上传代码不是很勤奋，所以最后只能做设计师了。</p>\n<p>有一天我看着自己的活跃度格子沉思良久，慢慢地一个想法在我的脑海浮现：<strong>活跃度也是格子啊，我可以用这个活跃度的格子做一件格子衬衣啊。每个程序员的活跃度都不一样，那每个程序员就拥有一件独一无二的格子衬衣啦。这样，就再也不会有格子衬衣撞衫的尴尬啦</strong>。</p>\n<p>我很快画好了设计图，看起来还不错嘛。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/ebb608ed9b453a468fc0fe23d13f47cb/8ec0a/result.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 80.625%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"result\"\n        title=\"result\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/ebb608ed9b453a468fc0fe23d13f47cb/c08c5/result.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/ebb608ed9b453a468fc0fe23d13f47cb/0913d/result.jpg 160w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/ebb608ed9b453a468fc0fe23d13f47cb/cb69c/result.jpg 320w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/ebb608ed9b453a468fc0fe23d13f47cb/c08c5/result.jpg 640w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/ebb608ed9b453a468fc0fe23d13f47cb/6a068/result.jpg 960w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/ebb608ed9b453a468fc0fe23d13f47cb/eea4a/result.jpg 1280w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/ebb608ed9b453a468fc0fe23d13f47cb/8ec0a/result.jpg 2560w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>趁着灵感还在，我赶紧写了个小程序，帮助程序员快速生成自己的格子衬衣。当天晚上开始写，我第二天天亮时就写好了。</p>\n<p>如果你是程序员，可以扫描上面的小程序码生成自己的格子衬衣。当然了，如果你不是程序员或者没有 Github 账号的话是没法使用的，因为你要输入 Github ID 才可以生成自己的格子衫。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"我要给每个程序员做一件独一无二的格子衬衣","date":"2019/03/06","description":"把 Github 的活跃度格子画在你的衬衣上。","color":"#FFF","cover":"checked-shirt.jpg","demo":"demos/checked-shirt.png","demoText":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/creative/checked-shift/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/creative/brain-hole/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"脑洞没边儿"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/projects/designsystem/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"设计系统"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["63159454"]}